entity.sql_stmt: SELECT STRFTIME ('%d/%m/%Y',[ExecutionDetail].[timestamp]) Dates,[ReportDetail].[reportId] AS reportId, COUNT([ReportDetail].[reportId]) ReportsCount FROM [ExecutionDetail] INNER JOIN [ReportDetail] ON ( [ExecutionDetail].[auditId] = [ReportDetail].[auditId] ) GROUP BY [ReportDetail].[reportId] ORDER BY 2 DESC -- '%m/%d/%Y''%d/%m/%Y'

SELECT [Audit].[id] AS id, [Audit].[userId] AS userId, [Audit].[hostId] AS hostId, E1.[timestamp] AS timestamp, E1.[transactionId] AS transactionId, E1.[transactionType] AS transactionType, [ReportDetail].[reportId] AS reportId, [ReportDetail].[reportType] AS reportType, [ReportDetail].[auditId] AS auditId, E1.[auditId] AS auditId FROM [Audit] INNER JOIN [ReportDetail] ON ( [Audit].[id] = [ReportDetail].[auditId] ) INNER JOIN [ExecutionDetail] E1 ON ( [ReportDetail].[auditId] = E1.[auditId] ) WHERE E1.[transactionType] = 'Report Execution Begins' AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM [ExecutionDetail] E2 WHERE E1.[auditId] = E2.[auditId] AND E2.[transactionType] = 'Report Execution Ends') ORDER BY [Audit].[id] ASC

SELECT STRFTIME ('%d/%m/%Y',E1.[timestamp]) ExecutionDate, [Audit].[id] AS id, [Audit].[userId] AS userId, [Audit].[hostId] AS hostId, E1.[timestamp] AS Starttimestamp, E1.[transactionId] AS transactionId, E1.[transactionType] AS transactionType, [ReportDetail].[reportId] AS reportId, [ReportDetail].[reportType] AS reportType, [ReportDetail].[auditId] AS auditId, E2.[timestamp] AS Endtimestamp, (( JulianDay(E2.[timestamp]) - JulianDay(E1.[timestamp]) ) * 86400.0) AS ExecutionSeconds FROM [Audit] INNER JOIN [ReportDetail] ON ( [Audit].[id] = [ReportDetail].[auditId] ) INNER JOIN [ExecutionDetail] E1 ON ( [ReportDetail].[auditId] = E1.[auditId] AND E1.[transactionType] = 'Report Execution Begins' ) INNER JOIN [ExecutionDetail] E2 ON ( E2.[auditId] = E1.[auditId] AND E2.[transactionType] = 'Report Execution Ends' ) ORDER BY 11 DESC
